Description:
Stunning brand new home. No need to build - ready now!
Take advantage of this wonderful opportunity to secure a brand new home with absolutely nothing more to do. No need to go through the hassle of building when you can purchase this stunning 4 bedroom home now and move in before Xmas!
Situated on a generous allotment this delightful property will appeal to a variety of buyers including first home owners, investors and families. Features include an attractive facade large well equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances including 900mm freestanding oven, range hood and dishwasher. Adjoining open plan meals and family area compliment easy living, while a second living area provides space for the kids rumpus or home theatre room.
Master bedroom offers a large WIR and en-suite and is completed with quality plantation shutters for an added touch of class. A further 3 bedrooms (all with BIRs) and central bathroom complete with bath and separate shower provide for great family living. Quality fixtures and fittings throughout the home are sure to impress as is the private outdoor entertaining area adjacent to the kitchen and accessed via large glass sliding doors.
A good size north facing backyard offers a safe and secure environment for children, while double gates at the side of the home provide additional access for the caravan, boat or trailer.
Rest assured, nothing has been spared with this home. It is completed in neutral tones, lush carpets and polished tiles and offers an array of additional extras including window furnishings, split system cooling, ducted heating, quality fencing, fully landscaped, watering system, remote DLUG with internal access, TV antenna and much more!
An excellent opportunity awaits the astute purchaser looking for low maintenance living and a brand new home finished to exacting standards. Inspect now.

Description:
Modern Living at its Best
On entry a wide tiled hallway welcomes you, opening out to a formal lounge with an outlook towards the reserve.
Double door entry to the study or possibly the home entertainment centre.
Free flowing open plan tiled kitchen, dining & living area.
For the aspiring chef the kitchen features glass splash backs, stainless steel 900mm free standing oven with gas hotplates, stainless dishwasher, stone bench tops.
The dining area would host even the largest of family dinner settings.
The under roof line alfresco area features bold brick pillars & mains capped gas point so you'll never run out of gas at your next BBQ.
The main family area is wide & deep enough to allow flexible lounge configurations.
The central bathroom & bedrooms are located off a separate passage way.
Located to the rear of the house the master bedroom is the ultimate parents retreat & designed to accommodate a sitting area or private study. The walk in robe & ensuite are of generous proportions.
This home was designed for entertaining living with a low maintenance front yard so you have more time to do the things you love.
Double garage with internal access.
Features include zoned ducted heating, air conditioning double pantry.
Located in a quiet cul-de-sac with open parkland with modern play equipment just a short walk away.
